<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="hero hero--subtle">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <span class="eyebrow">POS Software</span>
          <h1>Voice-first POS software for teams that want a pilot-ready stack</h1>
          <p>Bhojan Mitra software unifies voice ordering, AI-driven recommendations, and real-time kitchen routing. Join the pilot to co-design modules that fit your menu, workflows, and language mix.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="https://billing.aarohitavigyan.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Apply for the software pilot</a>
            <a href="#modules" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">See planned modules</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <span>Multilingual &amp; accent-aware voice flow</span>
            <span>Kitchen display + printer orchestration roadmap</span>
            <span>Analytics tuned with founding partners</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="modules" class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Core modules</span>
        <h2>Everything runs on one AI + IoT-ready foundation</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">We’re shipping the following software modules with and for our first five partner restaurants.</p>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Voice Ordering Engine</h3>
            <p>Conversational ordering trained on Indian restaurant dialogs, code-mixing, and modifiers so tickets are captured correctly the first time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Kitchen Routing &amp; KDS</h3>
            <p>Route tickets to the right station, highlight modifiers, and sync prep timers across displays and printers — pilot partners help refine flows.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Menu &amp; Inventory Sync</h3>
            <p>Edit menus once and push updates to voice prompts, QR menus, and billing. Real-time stock insights prevent out-of-stock orders.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Analytics Workspace</h3>
            <p>Dashboards for sales, covers, menu performance, and staff productivity. Founding partners influence KPIs and report templates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ecosystem">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Pilot roadmap</span>
        <h2>Shape the timeline with us</h2>
        <div class="ecosystem-grid">
          <div class="eco-card">
            <h3>Quarter 1 — Foundations</h3>
            <p>Voice engine tuning, menu builder, and realtime ticket pipeline. Partners get weekly drops, issue tracking, and direct engineering access.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-card featured">
            <h3>Quarter 2 — Analytics &amp; Reporting</h3>
            <p>Menu insights, team performance, custom exports. We’ll run workshops with pilot restaurants to refine the dashboard layouts.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-card">
            <h3>Quarter 3 — Automations</h3>
            <p>Inventory alerts, upsell nudges, and loyalty hooks integrate into the voice flow. Help us validate the automations that matter most.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">POS software FAQs</span>
        <h2>Questions operators ask about Bhojan Mitra POS software</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3>Does the software work with my existing POS hardware?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Bhojan Mitra runs on browsers, tablets, and our dedicated POS machine. We map printers and kitchen displays so you can migrate without downtime.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can I manage multiple outlets in one dashboard?</h3>
            <p>Multi-location controls are included in the pilot. You can segment menus, pricing, and analytics per outlet while sharing a single account.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3>Is Bhojan Mitra POS software GST compliant?</h3>
            <p>Yes. We generate GST-ready invoices, support custom tax slabs, and export data that plugs straight into your accounting workflow.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Want the software running in your restaurant?</h2>
        <p>Tell us about your current stack and we’ll map a pilot rollout plan together.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Apply for access</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">View founding partner plans</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
